[size=5][b]âœ¨ What is SantaHatItem?[/b][/size]

This mod makes the Santa Hat available as a wearable clothing item for players. The Santa Hat was originally added to the game for dealer NPCs only, but now you can purchase and wear it yourself!

[size=5][b]ğŸ Features[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][b]Wearable Santa Hat[/b]: Purchase and equip the festive Santa Hat as a clothing item
[*][b]Shop Integration[/b]: Automatically added to compatible clothing shops
[*][b]Custom Icon Generation[/b]: Generates an accurate preview icon using your player's appearance
[*][b]No Configuration Required[/b]: Works immediately after installation
[/list]

[size=5][b]ğŸ“¦ Installation[/b][/size]

[list=1]
[*]Download the latest [b]SantaHatItem.dll[/b] from the Files section
[*]Place it in your game's [font=Courier New]Mods[/font] folder
[*]Launch the game - the Santa Hat will be available in clothing shops!
[/list]

[size=5][b]ğŸ›’ How to Use[/b][/size]

Once installed, visit any clothing shop that sells accessories. The Santa Hat will appear as a red-labeled item:

[list]
[*][b]Price[/b]: $100
[*][b]Weight[/b]: 0.5kg
[*][b]Keywords[/b]: hat, cap, santa, christmas, holiday
[/list]

Simply purchase it like any other clothing item and equip it from your inventory!

