[size=5][b]ğŸ’¡ Technical Details[/b][/size]

This mod uses S1API's ClothingItemCreator to clone the existing "cap" item definition and configure it with the Santa Hat accessory asset. The icon is generated dynamically using your player's actual appearance for an accurate preview.

